creator: Thomas Moore
description:
LibriVox recording of Farewell -- But Whenever -- by Thomas Moore.

Read in English by Bruce Kachuk; Ian King; Jason Mills; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn; Marina Tsung; and Rosslyn Carlyle.

Librivox volunteers bring you seven readings of Farewell! – But Whenever – by Thomas Moore. This is the fortnightly poetry project for October 12, 2014.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (6MB)
